des:
This fun skill allows the users to ask Alexa about new ideas to resolve issues with their girlfriend.

Instructions:

Invoke the skill by saying: Alexa, Open Angry Girlfriend and Alexa will give you a random suggestion, that you could use.

You could also say, Alexa, Ask Angry Girlfriend for Guidance.
